{"TopicId":203082,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.12.x] ToggleLadderExit (TLE)","CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T18:38:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-16T18:38:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nKSP 1.11 got a new option in the overall game settings to control whether Kerbals can walk/slide off of the end of ladders.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found that it would be useful to be able to toggle this on the fly, ergo this mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EToggle Ladder Exit\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA simple little mod which allows toggling the new system-wide setting which prevents Kerbals from walking or sliding off the end of ladders.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EUsage\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nA toolbar button is provided, as well as a hotkey which does a momentary toggle. \u00A0The Toolbar Button shows the current state of the setting\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nPressing the hotkey (default is letter \u003Cstrong\u003EL\u003C/strong\u003E) will toggle the setting as long as the hotkey is depressed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHotkey Configuration\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nKeybinding can be changed by editing a file: \u00A0ToggleLadderExit/PluginData/keybind.cfg\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nThis file is created after the first time the mod is run, and is set with a default value of \u0022L\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nNote: By not distributing the file, any local changes will be preserved.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nIf you\u0027d like to create the file before running the first time, the contents will need to be:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003ETOGGLELADDEREXIT\n{\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0keycode = L\n}\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EToolbar Button\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe toolbar button looks like this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nOption is enabled (Kerbals cannot climb past end of ladder):\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022eWFI3hX.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002296.88\u0022 height=\u002293\u0022 width=\u002296\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/eWFI3hX.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-left:40px;\u0022\u003E\nOption is disabled:\u00A0\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022td5DTGp.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002298.91\u0022 height=\u002291\u0022 width=\u002292\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/td5DTGp.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003EDependencies\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/170747-141-click-through-blocker/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EClick Through Blocker\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/169509-141-toolbar-controller-for-modders/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EToolbarController\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAvailability\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nSource Code:\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ToggleLadderExit\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ToggleLadderExit\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDownload:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ToggleLadderExit/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/linuxgurugamer/ToggleLadderExit/releases\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLicense:\u00A0 MIT\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nAvailable via \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-06-16T18:59:29Z\u0022 title=\u002206/16/2021 06:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJune 16, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by linuxgurugamer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-17T18:27:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew release, 0.0.1.1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nAdded AssemblyFileVersion\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUpdated version file for 1.12\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"}]}